{"tid":2506071,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"佔中九子上訴案 上訴庭本周五頒判詞","createTime":"2021-04-27T05:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T08:16:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"be91cce0901a9e4ae2d242aaac4aa5c704be8d39","tid":2506071,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T05:35:58.000Z","msg":"2014年佔領運動，「佔中三子」戴耀廷、陳健民、朱耀明與另外六名學生及政治領袖，前年被裁定串謀與煽惑公眾妨擾等罪名成立，當中四人被判即時入獄，其餘被判緩刑或接受社會服務令。他們分別就定罪及刑期提出上訴。上訴庭上月初聽罷陳詞後，將於本周五（30日）頒下判詞。<br />\n<br />\n案件由上訴庭副庭長麥機智、原訟庭法官潘敏琦及彭寶琴處理。<br />\n<br />\n代表戴耀廷的律師張達明早前於上訴聆訊中表示，三子並無犯罪意圖。法庭或許會認為三人天真及不設實際，「但他們不應因為天真而被定罪」。張更強調，三子只是「串謀啟發香港人」。<br />\n<br />\n「佔中三子」原定佔領運動於2014年10月1日在中環舉行，張達明庭上陳詞指，「佔中」原定的日期及地點都是經過精心挑選，例如選擇在公眾假期舉行，以盡量減低對公眾構成的風險。惟事件最終演變至另一局面，日期提早至9月，而地點亦改為金鐘，場面不再受他們三人控制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210427/LR6MGMXRYJC6HAD2XQTBOQOUVM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210427%2FLR6MGMXRYJC6HAD2XQTBOQOUVM%2F&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oOoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=c9251bc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210427%2FLR6MGMXRYJC6HAD2XQTBOQOUVM%2F&h=9d275540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210427/LR6MGMXRYJC6HAD2XQTBOQOUVM/</a>"},{"pid":"c1ad7658b22c7555f4fa6d8cb8ec8dfb16a9d1ee","tid":2506071,"uid":275243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T05:44:20.000Z","msg":"戴生無啦啦被撤保都保到咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更何況又係加刑庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a2b734f72d50833d2633f4ea488c0233139df6","tid":2506071,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T05:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2efdf0c2828eb74f200daa6aa79aa36b5e92ec","tid":2506071,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T08:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}